ygData.messageBody:
> From: imari_dellimore@...
>
> As far as your info on the Gorge spawn goes. It conforms to
> my experience.
> Only thing I would add is that the 72-80 minte spawn seems to
> have a much wider
> range than that - sometimes you wont get a double spawn for
> more than 2 hours.
>

FYI, any spawn in the game can spawn nothing for a spawn cycle. That is
what you are seeing. Some, like the Goblin Alchemist in Permafrost, are
more likely to spawn nothing for a cycle. I.e. after the 25 min spawn, it
*will* spawn, but it is the "nothing" place holder. It's *very* annoying to
be sure.

Astur il'Ayan, Cleric of Brell
SCARAB on Solusek Ro
